Run Hedgehog property tests

Usage: cargo hedgehog [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  test      Run property tests (default)
  report    Generate test report
  coverage  Show test coverage
  discover  Discover property tests in the current project
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -t, --test <TEST>  Test name pattern to run
  -v, --verbose      Enable verbose output
      --show-all     Show all generated values (very verbose)
      --derive       Enable derive feature
      --release      Run tests in release mode
  -h, --help         Print help
